{"tid":1327841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"家父去銀髮族遊行見黑警混人群影大頭 大家小心！","createTime":"2019-07-17T17:51:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T19:06:52.000Z","uid":145488,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"25fa42c8af45b204458535127b3c09c4627f74ac","tid":1327841,"uid":145488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:51:04.000Z","msg":"話說家中兩老今日去咗銀髮族遊行<br />\n大會既dress code係白衫黑褲<br />\n但有兩個後生仔黑衫有個戴黑超<br />\n家父開頭以為係外國遊客湊熱鬧<br />\n點知見到兩條友係咁影人大頭<br />\n當時就係有個反對婆婆同現場嗌交時候發現到<br />\n然後家父突然勇武大叫「阿sir 喂 你好」<br />\n個兩隻黑警即刻呆咗唔知點反應<br />\n家父再大叫「阿sir」<br />\n嚇到兩隻黑警落荒而逃<br />\n<br />\n家父因爲無ac叫我要同大家講<br />\n仆街黑警連老友記遊行都唔放過<br />\n大家一定要小心留意便衣黑警影大頭！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZCLCx6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZCLCx6.png&h=a3e7d19f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5iLUvS7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5iLUvS7.png&h=8d301fb6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8gSDc6t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8gSDc6t.png&h=a1b94192&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7zPujMu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7zPujMu.png&h=d83503b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2cf29b28262682f53bf11d82d171395967e25f89","tid":1327841,"uid":61999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:52:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1bff896f94912a78f5706b6641221663c2fe204","tid":1327841,"uid":61999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:53:03.000Z","msg":"認人起底"},{"pid":"05a9fbe5bcd9f91a708bb43239d28a8e8a324db5","tid":1327841,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:53:34.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"85cca21f938275ee6a15c9fbd768ff10f50a1615","tid":1327841,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T17:56:31.000Z","msg":"push<img src=